Terra Energy Partners

 

































Corsa





















ABOUT TERRA ENERGY PARTNERS






Terra is an independent U.S onshore oil and gas exploration and production company growing through mergers and acquisitions to create value.
Headquartered in Houston, Terra pursues the acquisition and development of legacy producing oil and gas assets in North America. The team is led by Michael Land, an experienced E&P operations and commercial manager, and funded through Kayne Private Energy Income Fund, L.P.


BUILT ON A STRONG FOUNDATION









 
Mission


To acquire quality U.S. onshore assets with strong, long-term potential and opportunity for value creation





 
Vision


To operate a successful oil and gas company that delivers value to our investors





 
Values


Integrity, Safety, Accountability, Efficiency





 


 
Corporate Governance


 Terra Energy Partners promotes effective corporate governance by implementing responsible policies and management systems to reinforce business practices that are consistently sound, highly principled and transparent. 

 
 


 
Safety


 Safety is fundamental to our business. We aim to integrate programs and systems that prevent and mitigate incidents and reduce risks to our employees, contractors and communities where we operate. 

 







 


 
Environment


 We strive to minimize our operational footprint, protect ecosystems and implement conservation practices, making stewardship of the environment a responsibility of each member of our workforce. 

 
 


 
Economic & Social Development


 We work to strengthen the economies where we operate by investing time and resources in programs and initiatives that develop the sustainability of local communities. 

 







Terra Energy Partners is an experienced team with a proven track record in cost-efficient operations and creating value in existing and emerging assets







WHO WE ARE





We are a team of experienced, successful E&P and financial professionals





