TERRA ENERGY PARTNERS IS GROWING!

Terra is looking to hire individuals of character with special skills in onshore E&P with a desire to grow with an entrepreneurial company. If you meet our qualifications, we invite you to apply to one or more of our available positions.



Terra is an equal opportunity employer (M/F/D/V) and promotes the hiring of U.S. military veterans. Programs that support our efforts include the incorporation of military service toward Paid Time Off accrual.




To learn more about our competitive benefits package, click here.


View available Positions

 
 


TERRA ENERGY PARTNERS IS AN EQUAL OPPORTUNITY EMPLOYER.
Job postings are normally open for applications for a 2 week period; however, market conditions may warrant shorter or longer posting periods than indicated.
Resumes submitted to this website by a third party will be considered unsolicited and will become the property of Terra. Terra will not be obligated to pay a referral fee for the hiring of a candidate by means of an unsolicited resume submitted directly or indirectly through this site or any other means. Terra only pays for third-party referrals for resumes requested by the Human Resources department from our current vendors.




