terra energy resources ltd
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Waste & Environ Svcs & Equip
Sub-Industry: Waste Management
Terra Energy Resources, Ltd. engages in the process of polymer based recycling and reformation activities. The company produces and sells various kinds of oil based polymer materials to manufacturers for re-use. Terra Energy serves clients in the United States.




