			Company Description 
		


                Terra Energy Resources Ltd. engages in the process of polymer based recycling and reformation. The company produces different oil based polymer materials that are sent back to manufacturers for re use. Terra Energy Resources was founded on April 7, 2004 and is headquartered in New York, NY.
            




